      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="34400231">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/iamspringday/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u45156547-6.jpg" alt="慕月薇涵" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/34400231/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/34400231/" class="">退之诗说</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/iamspringday/" class=" " title="慕月薇涵">慕月薇涵</a>
                (生如夏花之绚烂)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="34400231">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">人最难得是个性强而又了解人情。                </span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2015-02-26 00:16</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">3人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                人最难得是个性强而又了解人情。                
